---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layout/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../../../components/Breadcrumb.astro';

const breadcrumbItems = [
  { href: '/', label: 'Home' },
  { href: '/what-we-do', label: 'What We Do' },
  { href: '/what-we-do/projects', label: 'Projects' },
  { href: '', label: 'Spreading Love and Hope' },
];
---

<BaseLayout title='Spreading Love and Hope'>
  <Breadcrumb items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <section class='py-13'>
    <div class='max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8'>
      <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8'>
        <!-- Main blog content -->
        <main class='md:col-span-7 lg:col-span-8'>
          <h1 class='text-4xl hist font-bold mb-4'>Spreading Love and Hope:</h1>
          <p class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-6'>A Success Story</p>

          <p class='mb-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed'>
            In a remarkable demonstration of compassion and community spirit,
            the Inuana Community Action Network (ICAN) recently organized a
            donation drive themed “Spreading Love and Hope” at the KOST
            Children’s Home in Homa Bay Town. The event served as a source of
            light and encouragement for the children, staff, and the wider
            community.
          </p>

          <p class='mb-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed'>
            The primary goal of the initiative was to provide essential support
            and uplift the well-being of the children residing at KOST. Thanks
            to the collective effort of generous donors and dedicated
            volunteers, ICAN distributed a range of vital items, including food
            supplies, sanitary products, clothing, and school materials. These
            contributions not only addressed immediate needs but also reinforced
            a sense of dignity, care, and belonging among the children.
          </p>

          <div class='my-6'>
            <img
              src='/gallery/22.jpg'
              alt='Partnership success'
              class='rounded w-full object-cover'
            />
          </div>

          <p class='mb-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed'>
            In addition to the donation drive, the event featured a
            tree-planting activity—an effort that underscored the importance of
            environmental responsibility. This hands-on initiative not only
            enhanced the natural beauty of the children’s home but also
            instilled values of environmental stewardship among the young
            residents.
          </p>
          <p class='mb-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed'>
            Beyond the tangible items, the drive offered something even more
            powerful: hope. It brought joy to the faces of the children, created
            meaningful connections, and served as a reminder of the impact that
            kindness, solidarity, and community-driven action can have on the
            lives of others.
          </p>
          <p class='mb-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed'>
            Thanks to the unwavering commitment of ICAN and the generosity of
            its supporters, the children at KOST now have more than just
            essential resources—they have renewed confidence in their future and
            the assurance that they are valued and supported by a caring
            community.
          </p>
          <p class='mb-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed'>
            This successful initiative stands as a compelling example of what
            can be achieved through unity, compassion, and purpose. As ICAN
            continues its mission, it remains dedicated to creating lasting
            change, one act of love and hope at a time.
          </p>
        </main>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <aside class='md:col-span-5 lg:col-span-4 space-y-6 mt-8 md:mt-0'>
          <div class='bg-gray-100 rounded overflow-hidden shadow'>
            <img
              src='/gallery/10.jpg'
              alt='Partnership success'
              class='w-full object-cover'
            />
          </div>
          <div class='bg-gray-100 rounded overflow-hidden shadow'>
            <img
              src='/gallery/20.jpg'
              alt='Partnership success'
              class='w-full object-cover'
            />
          </div>
          <div class='bg-gray-100 rounded overflow-hidden shadow'>
            <img
              src='/gallery/21.jpg'
              alt='Partnership success'
              class='w-full object-cover'
            />
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
